  "text": "Plate was imaged on a spinning disk confocal with Yokogawa CSUX A1 scan head, Andor iXon EMCCD camera and 20x Plan Apo Objective NA 0.79. Using the mManager high-content screening plugin 'HCS Site Generator' [CITATION_1] 49 fields per well were acquired for a mean cell number per well of 368 AE 12.",
